### Internal PMS — REST smoke tests (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP Client)
### Run top-to-bottom. Variables capture ids/tokens from earlier responses.

@host = http://localhost:4000

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

### Register (User A)
# @name registerA
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Alice", "email": "alice@example.com", "password": "password123" }

### Login (User A)
# @name loginA
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "alice@example.com", "password": "password123" }

@tokenA = {{loginA.response.body.data.token}}

### Me
GET {{host}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}

### Register (User B) — used to test membership
# @name registerB
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Bob", "email": "bob@example.com", "password": "password123" }

### Create a project
# @name createProject
POST {{host}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Website Revamp", "description": "Q3 marketing site" }

@projectId = {{createProject.response.body.data.project._id}}

### List my projects
GET {{host}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}

### Get one project
GET {{host}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}

### Add Bob as a member
POST {{host}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "bob@example.com", "role": "member" }

### Create a task
# @name createTask
POST {{host}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "title": "Design homepage", "description": "Hero + nav", "status": "todo" }

@taskId = {{createTask.response.body.data.task._id}}

### List tasks
GET {{host}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}

### Move task: Todo -> In Progress (the core real-time action)
PATCH {{host}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "in_progress" }

### Update task fields
PATCH {{host}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "title": "Design homepage (v2)" }

### Delete task
DELETE {{host}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
